# Homepage widget secrets for the `dashboard` Portainer stack.
#
# Copy these into Portainer's stack "Environment variables" editor (preferred),
# or place a filled-in .env beside the compose. They are injected into the
# container as HOMEPAGE_VAR_* and referenced in services.yaml as
# {{HOMEPAGE_VAR_NAME}}. They live ONLY on the box (never commit a filled copy).
#
# Where each value comes from:
#   JELLYFIN_KEY    -> Jellyfin -> Dashboard -> Advanced -> API Keys (create a NEW key)
#   JELLYSEERR_KEY  -> Jellyseerr -> Settings -> General (API Key)
#   QBIT_USERNAME   -> qBittorrent WebUI login username (NOT an API key)
#   QBIT_PASSWORD   -> qBittorrent WebUI login password
#   SONARR_KEY      -> Sonarr -> Settings -> General (existing API key)
#   RADARR_KEY      -> Radarr -> Settings -> General (existing API key)

HOMEPAGE_VAR_JELLYFIN_KEY=
HOMEPAGE_VAR_JELLYSEERR_KEY=
HOMEPAGE_VAR_QBIT_USERNAME=
HOMEPAGE_VAR_QBIT_PASSWORD=
HOMEPAGE_VAR_SONARR_KEY=
HOMEPAGE_VAR_RADARR_KEY=
